{"type": "article", "id": 9399, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-05-11T08:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3149, "name": "灯具"}, {"id": 2648, "name": "电动自行车"}, {"id": 3704, "name": "鞋子"}, {"id": 448, "name": "家具"}, {"id": 1358, "name": "玩偶"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}], "category": 17, "column": null, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607134931Y4FgUoxdTXq2GBer.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tBonton by Cristina Celestino\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t设计师 Cristina Celestino 受到耳环设计的启发，为意大利品牌 Torremato 设计了一款叫做 “Bonton” 的灯具，这款灯具系列的每一只灯上面都设计了一个蝶形旋钮，材料上选择的是铜，这些小旋钮和下面的吊灯配合在一起，看上去像是一个个形状各异的耳环。这个作品在米兰国际灯饰展进行了展出。这是<a href=\"http://www.torremato.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Torremato 的官方主页</a>，可以查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134914MKTacmEGS38xHPil.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51344743\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071349142NAYE4wTbnZtpldV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134915Zhr8sTDG7SNbkoRH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071349151JsjvmzS5MbGyfW8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68948655\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134916orLQETD1cvpnm36F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70782396\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134916ZHfE6gVPlxGivmM8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66870416\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tStan Smith 2015 by White Mountaineering &amp; Adidas Originals\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tStan Smith 小绿边鞋如今你大概是很难买到了，不过最近 White Mountaineering 和 Adidas Originals 为 Stan Smith 2015 系列带来了一个新成员。这款鞋子全身选用白色皮革，鞋头保持了漆皮的质感，十分美貌。这款鞋子将于 5 月 16 日开始登陆<a href=\"http://www.whitemountaineering.com/store/\" target=\"_blank\"> White Mountaineering 线上商店</a>，5 月 30 日起就可以在 Adidas Originals 门店买到了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134917Z8KbhIBQPnz1cH36.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134917YAKQRV6T9ZMxv1kp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071349170hxWA7cyGEsnLXVw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713491828ZCaP5Qcxrof9VE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tAdam by Springtime\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t阿姆斯特丹设计工作室 Springtime 最近推出了一款主要为学生设计的电动自行车。独特的是，他们把电动车的电池安置在了前面车把处，因此看起来和普通的自行车并无二致。此外，电池还具有减震功能。电池拆卸下来后，可以被当作扬声器。同时，这款车配备了行车电脑，可以通过触控屏幕导航。这款车采用的是碳纤维车架，装备有 20 英寸碳纤维轮圈，车身极其轻便，适合在城市里穿梭自如。这里有这个有着浪漫名字的<a href=\"http://springtime.amsterdam/\" target=\"_blank\">设计工作室的主页</a>，感兴趣的话，可以点进去看看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134918H7VWOxRrM1DaTt5F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134919xDlZs9SpJ16EA2hP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134919qRCsNXvilpFQ25jO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134920Drgy6MKlZoEFnVWh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071349211Ee5xKoCdZ3lvMuf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134921J4tzmR7ejHLMnBXc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tSingle-Curve Collection by Nendo\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t日本设计工作室 Nendo 最近和维也纳家具商 Gebrüder Thonet Vienna 合作推出了一款 “Single-Curve”（“单曲线”）曲木家具，包括凳子，高脚凳，餐桌等。这款作品在保持该品牌曲木特征的同时，加入 Nendo 的设计简约而精致的设计风格，直线与曲线的紧密结合反而让整体更具张力。Nendo 相信很多人已经很熟悉了，这里是 <a href=\"http://www.gebruederthonetvienna.com/index.php\" target=\"_blank\">Gebrüder Thonet Vienna 的官方主页</a>，可以查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134921O4hlLcwpMXsZf7Be.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071349222d4xDORcThNf3sJW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134922n8r9btexLS0EkBIY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134923HbF9ypmxAeJcBR5S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134923Ix8Vs6ePJfkGDZjX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071349243eksRdXHCpc1QYr0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134924OENSJYfQeoav4cI0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134924Nu7KyVjla51ZEdDI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tBigStuffed by Dana Muskat\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t现居巴黎的以色列时装设计师 Dana Muskat 试图为自己哥哥的女儿做一个独特的出生礼物，于是她做了一个大型的布艺玩偶，守护小侄女的降生。而设计师渐渐意识到，这种玩偶被各个年龄段的人喜爱，于是 “BigStuffed” 这个项目诞生。这些玩偶的原型都由 Dana Muskat 亲自设计，简单可爱，材料上采用天然的棉花和羊毛，颜色上以柔软温和的色调为主，带来满满的温暖和爱意。这些玩偶<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/BigStuffed\" target=\"_blank\">在这里可以买到</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071349257Wlqws4FdbRS90hQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071349256hNJWmyKTAZur49v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134926YGgaeWdNVKOhnZAJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134927W4uwJzckSXD9Kp8g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134927TRulJI1nwoUaVDK7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65520833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071349283DampSPN5sJuMFCG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.615625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071349288gQI5TFUWSH3Y6yj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134929eEhuXbxJ3gwCcZvo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134929jzZJI64T1nqpPyVF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134930URDieJY2Zd63HxaE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134930LRKPBi01X9FplGmU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}